data.description: SELLER IS WILLING TO NEGOTIATE A RATE BUY DOWN WITH THE RIGHT OFFER!!! Check out this adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Ormond beach close to Central Park. You'll love this open floor plan, high ceilings and beautiful wood burning fire place. The yard is fully fenced and ready for the pets and backyard barbques. This affordable home has a split bedroom plan, large closets,no carpet, and NO HOA. Centrally located and close to parks, shops and restaurants. Roof 2004, AC 2008, 2021 Hot Water Heater. All information taken from the tax record, and while deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed.
